'''AG-1G''' was the type of [[Quad laser cannon/Legends|quad laser cannon]] mounted on [[Mara Jade Skywalker]]'s personal [[Starship/Legends|starship]], the ''[[Jade Shadow]]''. While not as powerful as the [[AG-2G quad laser cannon/Legends|AG-2G quad laser cannons]] mounted on the [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|''Millennium Falcon'']], they were nonetheless quite potent when utilized by the ship's owner in combat.

